node.text: Here is PART 2 of the next edition of #SkipRidesTheTrollerCoaster - my responses to many of your questions FOR me and issues WITH me

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on August 20, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, beard, biceps and text that says 'V ATERCEL'.

node.text: Hey, LeBron … I just finished my second workout of the day. Weights kicked my butt. I know, you did three today. I’m just trying to keep up with you, King. I’ll run hard for an hour tomorrow morning and harder on Sunday. #StrivingForGreatness

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on August 20, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, footwear and indoor.

node.text: I can’t lose in these shoes. MJ FOREVER. #DripBayless

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2:02 RCA'.

node.text: Hey, LeBron …. I am UP here in LA, preparing for the day’s first workout and for Undisputed. You awake? Finishing your first workout? You there? LeBron???

node.text: HEY, LEBRON: IT’S 2:30 AM AND I’M STARTING MY FIRST WORKOUT OF THE DAY, RUNNING ON THE TREADMILL! WHERE YOU?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on August 19, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2:00 RC'.

node.text: Hey, LeBron, I am UP here in LA. Are you? I’m preparing for my first workout of the day. Are you? LeBron? WAKE UP, LEBRON!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on August 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says '2:02 RCA'.

node.text: The alarm just went off. I am UP here in LA, getting ready to kick some tail on Undisputed. The early bird gets the win. See you at 9:30 E on FS1.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on August 13, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, footwear and indoor.

node.text: I can’t lose in these shoes. MJ FOREVER. #DripBayless

node.text: I am BACK. Shannon is in trouble. Undisputed: NOW.
